'''Kikongo''' kele kimvuka ya [[bandinga ya kibantu]] na [[Afelika ya Kati]].

== Bandinga ya kikongo ==

Bandinga ya kikongo kele:

*H11 [[Kibembe]]
*H12 [[Kihangala]]
*H112 [[Kikamba]] na [[Kidondo]]
*H12 [[Kivili]]
*H13 [[Kikunyi]]
*H131 [[Kifuma]]
*H14 [[Kindingi]]
*H15 [[Kimboka]]
*H16 [[Kikongo]]
**H16a Kikongo ya sudi: [[Kisikongo]], [[Kimboma]], [[Kisongo]], [[Kisolongo]]
**H16b Kikongo ya kati: [[Kisundi]], [[Kimazinga]], [[Kimanyanga]]
**H16c [[Kiyombe]]
**H16d Kikongo ya lumonso: [[Kiwoyo]], [[Kibinda]] (to Kifyoti), [[Kikakongo]], [[Kikako]]
**H16e [[Kibwende]]
**H16f [[Kiladi]] (to Kilari)
**H16g Kikongo ya lunene: [[Kisantu]], [[Kintandu]]
**H16h Kikongo ya sudi-lunene: [[Kindibu]], [[Kinkanu]], [[Kizombo]], [[Kimbata]], [[Kipende]]
*Bandinga ya mpa
**H10a [[Kituba]] ya Kongo-Kinsasa to Kikongo ya leta
**H10b [[Kituba]] ya Kongo-Braza to Munukutuba
**H10c [[Kikongo ya Kuba]] to ''Habla Congo''

